			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S325">Mr. Udall of Colorado</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S330">Mr. Bennet</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSAF00">Committee on Agriculture, Nutrition, and Forestry</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
